    "attributes": {
        "action": "Hospital Treatment should not count towards School Absence figures",
        "additional_details": "We think days in the Hospital should not be reported as \"absent\" as there is no physical way attendance can be achieved or expected.",
        "background": "We think the Government should exclude days when a child is hospitalized and receiving treatment from their total annual class absence figure. We think there should be a clear distinction between a child reported as being ill vs a child receiving active hospital care.",
